b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/919-1
00:06:05.231 --> 00:06:06.094
<v Lina Čeponienė>aš bijau sumeluot.</v>

b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/935-0
00:06:06.984 --> 00:06:10.021
<v Lina Čeponienė>Bet man atrodo,
