b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/6757-1
00:47:39.627 --> 00:47:40.374
<v Lina Čeponienė>elementai.</v>

b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/6776-0
00:47:41.374 --> 00:47:44.554
<v Lina Čeponienė>Tai yra,
