b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/6776-1
00:47:44.554 --> 00:47:45.954
<v Lina Čeponienė>elementas, parodys aš.</v>

b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/6834-0
00:47:47.254 --> 00:47:51.116
<v Lina Čeponienė>Jeigu man atrodo,
