b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/6879-0
00:48:27.554 --> 00:48:29.914
<v Lina Čeponienė>Tai yra darau display.</v>

b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/6929-0
00:48:31.714 --> 00:48:36.777
<v Lina Čeponienė>Elements ir galiu pasirinkti,
