b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/6929-4
00:48:50.718 --> 00:48:52.244
<v Lina Čeponienė>Ką dar galiu padaryti?</v>

b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/6932-0
00:48:53.544 --> 00:48:54.534
<v Lina Čeponienė>Tai galiu.</v>

b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/6956-0
00:48:55.244 --> 00:48:59.605
<v Lina Čeponienė>Ištraukti kaip susijusius elementus,
