b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/6981-0
00:49:16.674 --> 00:49:17.854
<v Lina Čeponienė>Ir dabar atrodys va taip.</v>

b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/7032-0
00:49:20.944 --> 00:49:24.433
<v Lina Čeponienė>Nežinau, ar matot, jis paėmė mano modelis,
