b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/7160-0
00:50:45.724 --> 00:50:46.804
<v Lina Čeponienė>Klasikinė sako, d.</v>

b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/7165-0
00:50:47.974 --> 00:50:49.944
