b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/7172-0
00:50:53.934 --> 00:50:54.404
<v Lina Čeponienė>Ar ne?</v>

b138ea6f-cf1f-4554-9ad1-97678ed98c5e/7176-0
